text: Valeriya Rylova (born 22 November 1987) is a Kazakhstani volleyball player. She played at the 2014 Asian Games, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2017 Asian Women's Club Volleyball Championship. She played for VC Astana. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Kazakhstani volleyball players Category:Living people
